description: Creates a service principal in the directory.

parameters.description: Parameters to create a service principal.

displayname.description: The display name for the service principal.

homepage.description: The URL to the homepage of the associated application.

approleassignmentrequired.description: Specifies whether an AppRoleAssignment to a user or group is required before Azure AD will issue a user or access token to the application.

replyurls.description: A collection of reply URLs for the service principal.

publishername.description: The display name of the tenant in which the associated application is specified.

serviceprincipalnames.description: A collection of service principal names.
